'''Bent Gavler''' was a resident of [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] on [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]], and a friend of the family of eleven-year-old [[Allania Jakien]]. He ran a [[trading post]].

==Biography==
After Jakien had a harrowing experience avoiding [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] and witnessing [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] during the evacuation of Cloud City, she ran into Gavler in the upper plaza. Gavler took her in his arms and consoled her panicked crying. He reunited her with her family, and they all departed Bespin on a crowded transport.

